{"tid":1868141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大批內地旅客申請延長逗留在港期限","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca84bfe4b7465c95ce56cb4feed834bb58984ec","tid":1868141,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"在入境事務大樓，大批內地旅客申請延長逗留在港期限。<br />\n<br />\n在入境事務大樓五樓延期逗留組的櫃台外，坐滿申請延期留港的人，當中不少是內地旅客。<br />\n<br />\n內地一般自由行來港簽證留港限期是七天，當局在2月1日起暫停發出自由行簽證，最後一批在這一兩天到期，如要延長留在時間，要向入境處申請獲得批准；持其他種類簽證的內地人如要延長留港，亦要獲得批准。<br />\n<br />\n有安徽旅客說當地疫情嚴峻、交通亦癱瘓，計劃申請留在香港多一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379721&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=4ef9dbbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379721&h=bba51e3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=379721</a>"}]}